    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "FilesCenter是核心PLC，用深色突出；WriterTop虽然也是PLC逻辑，但属于边缘计算节点，用稍浅的颜色区分。四个TelemetryStream是同等的数据流模块。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FilesCenter",
        "WriterTop",
        "IoT_Industrial_TelemetryStream",
        "core",
        "mod"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先画出五个主要节点：顶部WriterTop、左侧ScholarLeft、右侧VisRight、底部CodeBottom，中心FilesCenter。四个TelemetryStream用mod样式，FilesCenter用core样式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "WriterTop",
        "ScholarLeft",
        "VisRight",
