      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：ScholarLeft→WriterTop，WriterTop→CodeBottom，CodeBottom→VisRight，VisRight→WriterTop，这个交叉协同对吗？还有中心FilesCenter到四个边缘都是双向？",
